---
// MCP Manager Features Component
---

<section id="features" class="py-24 sm:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:text-center">
      <h2 class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-primary">Features</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground sm:text-4xl">
        Everything you need to manage MCP servers
      </p>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-muted-foreground">
        MCP Manager provides comprehensive tools for managing Model Context Protocol servers with automation, monitoring, and maintenance capabilities.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-2xl sm:mt-20 lg:mt-24 lg:max-w-4xl">
      <dl class="grid max-w-xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-10 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-y-16">
        <div class="relative pl-16">
          <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-foreground">
            <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary">
              <span class="text-primary-foreground">🔧</span>
            </div>
            Global Configuration
          </dt>
          <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-muted-foreground">
            Centralized MCP server setup for all Claude Code projects with automatic conflict resolution and migration tools.
          </dd>
        </div>

        <div class="relative pl-16">
          <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-foreground">
            <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary">
              <span class="text-primary-foreground">📊</span>
            </div>
            Health Monitoring
          </dt>
          <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-muted-foreground">
            Real-time status checking, connectivity validation, and performance monitoring with detailed diagnostics.
          </dd>
        </div>

        <div class="relative pl-16">
          <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-foreground">
            <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary">
              <span class="text-primary-foreground">🔄</span>
            </div>
            Automated Updates
          </dt>
          <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-muted-foreground">
            Intelligent updating of MCP servers and dependencies with backup and rollback capabilities.
          </dd>
        </div>

        <div class="relative pl-16">
          <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-foreground">
            <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary">
              <span class="text-primary-foreground">🔍</span>
            </div>
            Configuration Audit
          </dt>
          <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-muted-foreground">
            Complete analysis of project-specific vs global configurations with migration assistance.
          </dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>